@node INSTALLATION "It's just too easy.."

@{b}Installation@{ub}

 It's very simple.

 1. Make sure @{"AmiTCP" LINK AMITCP_DESC} is running and that you have @{"Archie 38.1" LINK ARCHIE_DESC} installed.

 2. Make sure you have @{"RexxReqTools" LINK REXXREQ_DESC} and @{"FTPGet" LINK FTPGET_DESC} installed.

 3. Change to the GUI-Archie directory (wherever you unlha'd to)

 4. Type 'copy GUI-Archie inet:bin/'

 5. Type 'protect inet:bin/GUI-Archie swrd'

 6. That's it.

@endnode

